featured_reviews.review_id: I took level one Reiki with Myorei at this beautiful, peaceful space. Care and attention was made to ensure safe procedures. The duration of the course was scintillating, energizing and a great balance of learning, discussion, hands-on, and theory. Wonderful for all learner types. The take home readings were enlightening and informative. Myorei is a wonderful teacher and I am excited to learn more from her in future courses. I strongly recommend!

featured_reviews.review_id:
Thank you so much Myorei. Your teaching is helping me to learn and understand about reiki and also other techniques that can help me with self care and healing others.
Myorei is a zen meditation master and a reiki master teacher. Her teaching is very personalized. She also provides delicious light vegan meals during the break. Myorei is a very kind, warm and humorous person.
Thank you very much again for your teaching. I am looking forward to meeting you at the next level.

featured_reviews.review_id: My wife and I went to Myorei reiki for the level 1 session and it was fantastic. Myorei is so radiant of warmth and positive energy that  we really enjoyed our 7 hours training. We were able to connect ourself with some energies and were very surprised with the results. We are now doing our daily Reiki session at home and personally I feel my energy more balance. Merci Myorei for showing us the way.
